[[File:Mandalorian_Heavy_Suit.jpg|thumb|150px]]
The '''[[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] heavy suit''' was a stronger version of the [[Mandalorian combat suit]], providing protection to melee damage beyond the scope of what would be expected of a normal combat suit of that weight. This version was used by elite scouts and could be outfitted with various upgrades in addition to the combat suit's capabilities.
Its popularity continued through into the [[Dark Wars]] and was valued at 10,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] at that time.

